So Walk Medford and the Friends of the Community Path in Somerville and me and a handful of other people, because there apparently has been some movement on this, which due to the pandemic and other things, there weren't any public meetings about this.

332
00:25:47,483 --> 00:25:55,478
The concern the last time we talked about this, which was four or five years ago, was that they were planning on building it 12 feet wide.

