00:26:21,332 --> 00:26:25,853
significant hurdle possibly involving approval as far as the governor.

336
00:26:28,113 --> 00:26:38,195
And this is still I still haven't seen very much actual details on this.

337
00:26:39,375 --> 00:26:45,136
I don't think there's a easily accessible publicly available document.

338
00:26:45,156 --> 00:26:46,456
But

339
00:26:49,845 --> 00:27:10,641
The people that met mostly were kind of of the opinion that it would be worth trying to push for building it wider, even if that goes as far as delaying the project, because basically the planning would have to kind of back way, way, way up to build it wider.

