00:27:47,191 --> 00:27:55,576
And given that this is a pretty needed connection for the people who live, especially on the Everett end of it,

343
00:27:58,385 --> 00:28:16,651
I would like to hear from some of them whether they think it's a higher priority to slow down and try to figure out if there's a way to build a wider bridge or if it's more important to just hurry up and build the thing because they would really like to get across the river.

